===========================================
|ID|OPERATOR                     |NAME    |
-------------------------------------------
|0 |SORT                         |        |
|1 |└─HASH JOIN                  |        |
|2 |  ├─PX COORDINATOR           |        |
|3 |  │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR     |:EX10000|
|4 |  │   └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR|        |
|5 |  │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |ZT2     |
|6 |  └─PX COORDINATOR           |        |
